50|$|<b>Mirror</b> <b>nuclei</b> are nuclei {{where the}} number of protons of element one (Z1) equals {{the number of}} {{neutrons}} of element two (N2) {{and the number of}} protons of element two (Z2) equals the number of neutrons in element one (N1), such that the mass number is the same (A = N1 + Z1 = N2 + Z2).|$|E
